data.description: Take a look at this charming home located in Harrodsburg. This home offers, 2 bedrooms, 1 full bathroom, living room and eat in kitchen. This would be a great home for a first time buyer, investor or if you are looking to downsize. Conveniently located close to all the amenities Harrodsburg has to offer! Call or text to schedule your private showing today!
